Cheburashka and Gena the Crocodile are riding in the bus.<br>Cheburashka asks:<br>- Gena, who is that in the front with a steering wheel? <br>Gena replies:<br>- The driver.<br>And Cheburashka hears "beaver". They continue to ride.<br>Cheburashka:<br>- Gena, what are we riding in? <br>- In a bus.<br>Cheburashka hears "in a sausage". They ride some more and then the bus crashes into a tree.<br>Cheburashka asks:<br>- What have we just crashed into?<br>- Into a tree.<br>Cheburashka has heard "into a salad". A police officer approaches them. Cheburashka asks:<br>- Who's that?<br>- A police officer.<br>And he has heard "comrade with a small penis".<br>Cheburashka comes out of the bus and says:<br>- What the fuck do I need these big ears for if I can't hear shit?